---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="页面未找到" description="你访问的页面不存在或已被移动。" noindex>
  <div class="container-page section-space text-center">
    <p class="label-meta">404</p>
    <h1 class="mt-3 text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight">页面未找到</h1>
    <p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-md text-ink-600 dark:text-ink-300">
      链接可能已失效，或地址输入有误。你可以返回首页，或从导航进入博客、项目与工具。
    </p>
    <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3">
      <a href="/" class="btn-primary">返回首页</a>
      <a href="/blog/" class="btn-secondary">阅读博客</a>
      <a href="/projects/" class="btn-ghost">查看项目</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
